text: Sandringham is a village in Norfolk. Sandringham is famous because that is where Sandringham House and its estate are. Sandringham House is a holiday home of Queen Elizabeth II and several other people related to the English Royal Family. Near the house is the Royal Stud, a stud farm that houses many of the royal horses. The village was the birthplace of Diana, Princess of Wales.
